{'title': 'Naxalites Sabotage Vehicle At Road Construction Site In Gadchiroli District', 'publish time': '2023-02-28T10:39:49+00:00', 'update time': '2023-02-28T18:40:22+00:00', 'author': 'Alan Warsaw', 'images': ['https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/bfe82cb69fd6b38b3da208aafab5351e-800x445.jpg'], 'text': "![](https://www.redspark.nu/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/bfe82cb69fd6b38b3da208aafab5351e-800x445.jpg)\n\n**Gadchiroli District, February 28, 2023:** A squad of Naxalites set ablaze avehicle engaged in road construction work in Maharashtra's Gadchirolidistrict, police said on Tuesday.\n\nAccording to a police official, at around 11 pm on Monday, armed Naxalitescame to the construction site at Botanpundi-Visamundi road and set afire thevehicle, a mixer truck.\n\nAfter the incident came to light on Tuesday morning, the Tadgaon policeinspected the spot and registered a case.\n\n> Source : https://www.ptinews.com/news/national/maha-naxalites-burn-down-> vehicle-engaged-in-road-construction-in-gadchiroli-district/522922.html", 'tags': ['CPI (maoist)', 'CPI(maoist)', 'Gadchiroli', 'Gadchiroli district', 'India', 'Maharashtra', 'Maharashtra State', 'Naxal', 'naxalites', 'naxals', 'police', 'PPW in India'], 'categories': ['India', "People's War"], 'source': 'https://www.redspark.nu/en/peoples-war/naxalites-sabotage-vehicle-at-road-construction-site-in-gadchiroli-district/'}